LINK TO CAD This XY gantry for the HevORT integrates the same robustness philosophy as the previous HD (heavy duty) chapters. But this time around it multiplies the available power by a factor of TWO!

That's it! Four Stepper motors to make your HevORT ALL Wheel(corner) Drive.
Motors are place in a diagonal fashion for each belt reducing the path length between drive force to print head to a minimum.		 HD12 SPAWD
Short Path All Wheel Drive
